You can reduce the number of edge locations for COST REDUCTION.

Origin Groups(primary/secondary): 
  for high availability and do failover
  if the primary origin fails, the second one is used.
  
  
Region Level High Availability: 
  s3[Replication] + CloudFront 
  
Field Level encryption: 
  adds an additional layer of security along with HTTPS.
  only the eb server can decrypt it using the private key.
  data not accessible to the CF or the application load balancer. 
  
